title: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters dialog
OB: Default values are not shown in the Show Report Parameters dialog.
EB: When previewing the report and clicking the Show Report Parameters button, the expected result is that the default values are shown in the value box so that I can modify the parameter I want to change. However, the actual result is that in the Enter Parameters dialog, all values are empty. I expected to only modify one parameter but found that I had to input all values.
SR:
To reproduce the bug:
1. Preview the report.
2. Click the Show Report Parameters button.
